The MIT terms above cover the SOURCE CODE of this repository only.

  * tools/reference-python/
        The community project's `mercs2-mesh-pipeline-scripts.zip`, vendored UNMODIFIED
        from Mercenaries-Fan-Build/mercs2-wad-simulator so the byte-parity test has a
        specification to check against. Not this project's work; see that project for its
        terms.

  * src/texture.js
        A JavaScript port of that project's dds_to_ucfx_texture.py. The Mercenaries 2
        container layout it implements was reverse-engineered there.

